A man is in a critical condition after an apparent hijacking at Atlas Road in Kempton Park on Tuesday afternoon.It is believed that the man is in his 30&#8217;s. On arrival ER24 paramedics found the man lying on the side of the road.ER24 spokesperson Russel Meiring &#8220;ER24 paramedics assessed the man and found that he had sustained a gunshot wound to the arm as well as his face, leaving him in a critical condition&#8221;.The man was treated and was airlifted by a private medical helicopter to a private hospital in Johannesburg for further care.The details surrounding the incident are not yet known.-Aviwe Maxheke